Analysed one year(2000) data for calculating :
maximum temperature(TMax) 
Minimum tempreature(TMin)
Top 3 hotest weather stations
Top 3 coldest weather stations
Hottest station on a particular day from year range(2000 to 2002) with temperature value
coldest station on a particular day from year range(2000 to 2002) with temperature value

Dataset info:

https://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/data/ghcn/daily/by_year/
